{
  "texts": [
    "The final two parameters describe the eccentricity at SMBHB pairing {e 0 } and the density of the stellar environment {ζ 0 }.",
    "For the 18 parameters listed above, in the analysis presented here, we use the extended prior intervals listed in Table I of Chen et al. (2019).",
    "The main results of the inference are shown in Figs. 6 7 8.",
    "Figure 6 shows the marginalised posterior distribution for the normalization of the merger rate density ṅ0 from the agnostic model compared to an equivalent parameter derived from the astrophysically-informed model.",
    "The constraint on the amplitude of the signal imposes an informative constraint on the normalization of the SMBHB merger density."
  ]
}